years, even though its current feasibility is limited by the fact that its =
construction would require more matter than is available in our entire ecos=
ystem.=C2=A0
We=E2=80=99re looking for something similar in the digital realm: a way to =
harness the energy that successful Small Apps spit off when they get really=
