=A0
Protocols that let users carry their identity, data, and relationships acro=
ss Small Apps are a strong candidate. This is, of course, part of the premi=
se behind decentralized social protocols like Farcaster and Lens, and data =
protocols like Ceramic Network [ https://substack.com/redirect/5acdb4e9-bab=
b-4985-9fd4-7a456c7c449b?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKb=
qOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]. Ceramic (Not Boring Capital portfolio company) describe=
