</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 20px 0;"><span>If you assume that Small Apps </span><em>can</em><span>=
 get very big &#8211; acquire millions of users, generate millions of dolla=
rs &#8211; but typically </span><em>can&#8217;t</em><span> build a defensib=
le business, then you could design the business in a way that looks a lot l=
