le. Those users, and their data and relationships, are the prize here.&#160=
;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>You can keep the cash you pull in, the protocol=
 doesn&#8217;t care. It just wants those users and their data and/or relati=
onships. Facebook built a $600 billion business on the back of its 3 billio=
