the protocol&#8217;s upside over the long-term.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D=
"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">I=
mportantly, Small Apps that partner with and build on Growing Protocols don=
&#8217;t need to be &#8220;crypto&#8221; apps. In other words, the protocol=
