style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
px 0;">Just let the users use the product for the thing the product does be=
st, with the added benefit that they can up and leave to the next product o=
n the protocol and bring their connections and data with them.&#160;</p><p =
style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
px 0;"><span>Over time, Small App developers could leverage web3&#8217;s in=
herent </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/19afae3b-33b0-4eb8-b=
