8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: #404040; text-decoration: underline;">composa=
bility</a><span> to build products that work with each other. Other develop=
ers could build Super Apps composed of pieces of many of the best Small App=
s on the protocol. They might bake in crypto payments or other native featu=
res. But that&#8217;s besides the point of this post; that&#8217;s up to de=
velopers to figure out over time alongside other technical and economic imp=
lementation details.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size:=
 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">For this post, the point is =
simply to identify the trend towards Small Apps, the challenges and opportu=
nities that trend represents, and one potential solution.&#160;</p><h3 clas=
