 using underlying protocols and often provide user-friendly interfaces that=
 mask the complexities of the backend systems.</span></p><p style=3D"color:=
 #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>=
Protocols</strong><span>: Sets of rules and conventions for digital communi=
cation and data transfer. They establish the standards that enable differen=
t software systems, including applications, to interact and exchange inform=
ation.</span></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">SMTP is the email Protocol; Gmail, Outlook, and =
Superhuman are three email Applications. Because of SMTP, you can read the =
same email whether you&#8217;re using Gmail, Outlook, or Superhuman, and us=
ers of any email application can send emails to each other.</p></div></div>=
